extends AbstractCommandLink
implements javax.faces.component.behavior.ClientBehaviorHolder, MetaComponentResolver, AccesskeyProps, AjaxCommandProps, BypassProps, CoreProps, LinkProps

    The <a4j:commandLink> component is similar to the JavaServer Faces (JSF) <h:commandLink> component, except that it includes plugged-in Ajax behavior.
